# Statsig Documentation repo

This repo is the source for **https://docs.statsig.com**, powered by **Mintlify**. Full instructions are in `CLAUDE.md` — read it before making edits. Key facts are below.

## Stack and local dev

- **Framework:** Mintlify (no custom build system, no Next.js)
- **Local dev:** `mintlify dev` (install once: `npm i -g mintlify`)
- **Files:** always `.mdx` — never `.md`
- **Navigation:** `docs.json` → `navigation.tabs[].groups[].pages[]`
- **Snippets:** reusable content must live in `/snippets/` — import with `import X from '/snippets/...'`
- **Links:** root-relative, no extension — `/feature-flags/overview` not `../feature-flags/overview.mdx`
- **Redirects:** add to `docs.json` `redirects` array when moving or renaming a page
- **Spellcheck vocab:** `styles/config/vocabularies/Mintlify/accept.txt`

